    "patch_code": "public String chompBalanced(char open, char close) {\n    int start = -1;\n    int end = -1;\n    int depth = 0;\n    char last = 0;\n\n    do {\n        if (isEmpty()) break;\n        Character c = consume();\n        if ((last == 0 || last != ESC) && c.equals(open)) {\n            depth++;\n            if (start == -1)\n                start = pos;\n        }\n        else if (!isEmpty() && c.equals(close)){\n            depth--;\n            \n        }\n\n        if (depth > 0 && last != 0)\n            end = pos; \n        last = c;\n    } while (depth > 0);\n    \n    if(end==tokens.length()-1){\n        end--;\n        \n    }\n    return (end >= 0) ? tokens.substring(start, end) : \"\";\n}",
